{"tid":2232330,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"防毒軟件創辦人邁克菲(John McAfee)西班牙被捕","createTime":"2020-10-06T09:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T10:33:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8cb4ddcc4fc4804434e2a973d11ef7c88268c5","tid":2232330,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:59:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】電腦防毒軟件邁克菲創辦人在美國涉嫌逃稅被起訴，他於西班牙轉機時被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙警方消息表示，在英國出生的邁克菲上周六持英國護照抵達巴塞羅那，企圖轉機到土耳其伊斯坦布爾時被拘留，稍後將轉送馬德里接受引渡美國的聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n美國田納西州檢察部門指控邁克菲逃稅和詐騙。案情指，他2014年至2018年期間，涉嫌借用其他人名下的銀行和虛擬貨幣戶口，以及借用其他人名義置業、買車和遊艇，刻意隱瞞收取超過2300萬美元佣金，發放誤導的虛擬貨幣交易建議，罪成最高可被判囚30年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=408050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408050&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKMkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=faefa59a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408050&h=6c09315b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=408050</a>"},{"pid":"a21909e22b9f79cd5871f65d9f434b4ec7dd0cb0","tid":2232330,"uid":254450,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:01:58.000Z","msg":"呢個年代仲有咩人會特登買防毒軟件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c7a63121156013b725bf297ea92f807da98a4f","tid":2232330,"uid":227992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a21909e22b9f79cd5871f65d9f434b4ec7dd0cb0","tid":2232330,"uid":254450,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:01:58.000Z","msg":"呢個年代仲有咩人會特登買防毒軟件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" clas